posts.post_title: T3 Turkey Red Walter Johnson Ad Back Raw but Former PSA 1 - SOLD
posts.post_content:
I have a T3 Walter Johnson with the Turkey Red Ad Back. I purchased this card in raw form but at some point a previous owner cracked it out of a PSA 1 holder. Card presents extremely well. Asking $SOLD.
